name: Raven Le Faye - Pink
description:
Raven was a princess. I mean really, her day job was being a princess for children's parties:) 

Still trying to figure out what I'm doing here. I had such an amazing response to my first drop that my head is now full of ideas. If you like my work and you have any ideas, criticisms or whatever please feel free to hit me up on the Twitter account or website linked in my bio.
